<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n14148f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n14" href="#n14148f">N14 (VI.B.7)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n14all.htm#n14148f"> 148(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Rurick = 3 B</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>Three brothers</mark> with their followers were chosen: the eldest <mark>Rurik</mark> (O.N. Hroerekr), settled in Novgorod, the second in Bielo&ouml;zero, the third in Truvor in Izborsk. Three years later <mark>two of the brothers died and Rurik took control</mark> of the whole of the settlements, dividing the land among his men. <small> Allen Mawer, <a name="AMTV1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#AMTV1"><cite title="source">The Vikings</cite></a>, (1913) 74</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
